Package: crio
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2021-05-21
Title: CellRanger Input/Output
Authors@R: c(
        person("Aaron", "Lun", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "infinite.monkeys.with.keyboards@gmail.com"), 
        person("Jonathan", "Griffiths", role="ctb")
    )
Description: 
    Load CellRanger's output files into Bioconductor data structures, most typically a SingleCellExperiment containing assay values.
    Also supports writing to CellRanger formats.
Depends: SingleCellExperiment
